annotationA: FI08065p; Purine-nucleoside phosphorylase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: nucleoside metabolic process
annotationB: Guanine deaminase; Catalyzes the hydrolytic deamination of guanine, producing xanthine and ammonia. Also has 7,8-dihydropterin deaminase activity, which plays a role in synthesis of the red eye pigment aurodrosopterin
